Line is a vertex canvas instruction. It allows drawing of lines through points. This code shows how to
use/draw the extended line drawing such as circles, ellipses, rectangles and Bezier and so on.


Basic Approach:

1) import kivy
2) import kivy App
3) import Gridlayout
4) import widget
5) set minimum version(optional)
6) Create as much as widget class as needed
7) create the App class
8) return the widget/layout etc class
9) Run an instance of the class